  <title>Mail Filters — Davis Inbox Triage seed set (GL-018)</title>
  <!-- Import via Gmail: Settings > Filters and Blocked Addresses > Import filters.
       Every rule below trashes on arrival AND can be run against existing mail
       ("Also apply filter to matching conversations") to bulk-clear the backlog.
       These are the confirmed repeat PROMOTIONAL senders from the 2026 cleanup.
       NONE of these senders emit account/statement mail to this inbox, so
       trashing wholesale is safe. Senders with a marketing+account split
