  <!-- SOCIAL NOTIFICATIONS: LinkedIn notification streams. These are the
       notification EMAILS only - the actual invitations/messages live in
       LinkedIn itself, so trashing the emails loses nothing; Jeff actions
       connections and DMs in the app. This covers invitations, job listings,
       notifications, and message-recap emails. It does NOT touch a real
       person-to-person email that arrives from a non-notification address. -->
